{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:11:53.104830+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository's `profiles.toml` and `README.md`, the `vidpack` command ships with **three encoding profiles**:\n\n| Profile | Container | Video Codec | Audio Codec | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------------|-------------|-------|\n| **`web`** | `.mp4` | `libx264` (H.264) | `aac` | 720p at a target bitrate of 2 Mbps |\n| **`archive`** | `.mkv` | `libx265` (H.265/HEVC) | `flac` | Source resolution, CRF 18 (near-lossless quality) |\n| **`gif`** | `.gif` | *(palette-based, no traditional codec)* | *(none)* | 480px wide, 12 fps, single-pass palette generation |\n\nUsers can also edit `profiles.toml` to add or customize profiles (names must be lowercase ASCII). The profiles are loaded from that file at runtime, so the three above are the defaults that ship with the tool.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 391, "prompt_tokens": 4034, "total_tokens": 4425, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 159, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 3840}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 3840, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 194}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "e6f23ca0-acc8-464e-ad0d-78a9c0b726ce", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea424-62a1-7473-bb3d-6a9e83c4bb31-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4034, "output_tokens": 391, "total_tokens": 4425, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 3840}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 159}}}}]}}}
